    "en": {
      "title": "Money from ether is down",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Central Bank of Sri Lanka stated that the money flowing into the country through foreign workers has decreased by 51.6 percent in the first 6 months of this year compared to the first 6 months of last year.",
        "The Central Bank of Sri Lanka indicated that in the first 6 months of last year, Sri Lanka had received 3324.4 million US dollars in foreign labor remittances, and in the first 6 months of this year, it has dropped to 1609.9 million US dollars."
      ],
